longBusinessSummary: HAEMATO AG, together with its subsidiaries, operates in the pharmaceutical sector in Germany. The company distributes European imported drugs and medical products; and manufactures and distributes its own generic medicinal products. It provides pharmaceuticals in the areas of oncology, HIV/AIDS, rheumatism, neurology, and cardiovascular diseases; and products for aesthetic treatments. The company also develops and markets medical devices and medical technology products for aesthetic surgery and cosmetic dermatology. It serves wholesalers and pharmacies, as well as doctors, clinics, medical laboratories, and hospitals. The company was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in SchÃ¶nefeld, Germany.
